sequenceDiagram
    participant Buyer
    participant DALP as DALP Settlement Engine
    participant AssetLeg as Asset Contract
    participant CashLeg as Cash/Stablecoin Contract
    participant Chain as EVM Network

    Buyer->>DALP: Initiate DvP Settlement
    DALP->>DALP: Validate Both Parties
    Note over DALP: Check OnchainID claims<br/>Verify compliance rules<br/>Confirm asset availability
    DALP->>AssetLeg: Lock Asset Tokens
    DALP->>CashLeg: Lock Payment Amount
    DALP->>Chain: Submit Atomic Transaction
    Note over Chain: Both legs execute together<br/>or both revert together
    alt Settlement Success
        Chain-->>AssetLeg: Asset Transferred to Buyer
        Chain-->>CashLeg: Payment Transferred to Seller
        Chain-->>DALP: Settlement Confirmed
        DALP-->>Buyer: T+0 Settlement Complete
    else Settlement Failed
        Chain-->>DALP: Revert Both Legs
        DALP-->>Buyer: Settlement Reverted
    end
